Author: Swanabe
Text: Girl, pretty much same.   My ed absolutely developed because I grew up with two parents who are addicted to control, and older siblings who learned those shitty interpersonal skills from our parents.   To this day they try to control me, I’m 20fucking6 and they still feel entitled to have final say on everything in my life. It’s one of my main triggers.

Author: MeDasPenaAjena
Text: I feel the same. When I look at all my problems I’ve caused myself in life it’s always about control. To be honest could be ocd, I would see a doc. My brother didn’t get diagnosed until he was 20.
